social_posts.post_text: The proudest big sister ever. Thank you Jesus for this sweet baby + our growing family! Mini Magill coming June 2023 ♡
Big Sister was RIGHT! We love you + cannot wait to meet you, baby “brudder” ♡
The end is in sight for our Scottsdale AirBNB project. This “teen room” is going down as one of my favorite!

I am having a *pinch me* moment that this is my JOB. Thank you to my sweet clients for trusting me and their talented team for incredible execution! Thank you to all of you for cheering me on— this business + dream wouldn’t be what it is without you ♡

Now booking ☀️ This Scottsdale, AZ AirBNB is now available for your next trip! Full of color, pattern, and detailed decor less than a mile from Fashion Square Mall. This house is going down as one of my favorite projects, ever! Booking link available in my “Scottsdale” highlight.

I have goosebumps everywhere!!

I had to use this audio!! It’s too perfect for this kitchen featuring a grand 14ft island— a dream 💭

The sweetest “big boy” room for Weston! I have been dying to share this cozy, western inspired room. It was so fun creating this space for @thebrittkit! Britt is the ultimate boy mama and her little fam makes me so excited for baby brother!! 🤠

Sis on the slopes ⛷️🥹🫶🏼
Logan has been dreaming of this day since she was born!!

Does anyone else have a toddler who is unsatisfied by the answer to “how many days until my birthday?” or “how many days until the beach?” We brought back the simple + easy countdown ring to help! I used to make these as a kid and it’s such a fun activity for us to do together. She looks forward to ripping off a ring each morning! Linking the $6 package of colorful strips we used here: https://liketk.it/45PNB ♥️

“I was born with the ‘how hard could it be’ gene” —nothing could describe me better. 💀😂 I decided it was a great idea to wallpaper all four walls of the nursery in my third trimester… worth it! We finished wallpapering just in time for furniture to start arriving!! We are so excited for you baby brother ♡
we’re ready for you baby brother 🫶🏼

Mission: make Paw Patrol CUTE 🐾 
A modern + muted palette for my Paw Patrol loving girl! We had the best day celebrating our FOUR year old!! She has brought so much joy into our lives, and we partied accordingly 🥳

Vendors: 
balloon globe | @shopdeepsouthdesigns 
bounce house | @theokcparty 
kids chairs | @chelseyflintevents 
cake | @heysweetstuffokc 
cookies | @eileensnicholshillsok 
vinyls | @dizzywithexcitement

A house is just a house until you, fill it up ♡ 
Thank you Jesus for our growing family. We can’t wait to meet you so soon, baby brother!!
no greater joy ♡

It is finally baby month! Cherishing these photos with my first baby, forever 🫶🏼

Mamas— when did you go into labor with your second baby?? Same as the first, earlier, or later? 👀
Olsen Evan Magill ♡ 7lbs 12oz, born on June 15th at 1:44pm. He is absolutely perfect, and we are so in love!
Magill— party of four ♡

One month of Olsen Evan— we have spent so many hours in this little corner of his room! It makes me the happiest 🫶🏼

Here’s to sharing more project photos on my feed! I am itching to get back to designing and my creative outlet so soon, but for now you can find me in this rocker ☺️

Bubs first flight— he slept the entire time thanks to our @sollybaby wrap ✈️ 

The @sollybaby wrap has been my favorite item for both of my babies, especially during the newborn stage! Somedays it’s the only way I can get anything done.  The cute patterns are a bonus too!! Sharing a link for 10% off on my stories ♡

A look inside Olsen’s closet featuring our favorite @littleunicornofficial items— honorable mention goes to the BEST burp cloths ever 🏆 Linking everything we used to organize + our little unicorn items here: https://liketk.it/4fSjC @shop.ltk #liketkit #ad #littleunicorn 

We used the IKEA Boxael closet system here and the process from start to finish is saved to the “baby closet” highlight!

Thriving on the chaos + soaking in every single moment ♡ 

PS— I finally added bubs to my @tinytags necklace collection + I am so obsessed!

Life lately 🫶🏼

In the past two weeks we have traveled to California for one of our best friends wedding, spent so much family time together, I started easing myself back into work after maternity leave, and we bought and started reno on a rental property— reminding myself that while this season of life feels chaotic and exhausting, it’s also everything I’ve ever dreamed of!! 🙏🏼🥹🫶🏼

An office that makes WFH an easy task. 👩‍💻
I love how this colorful and bold this office turned out! Thank you @brene_mayes for trusting me with such a fun space ♡ 

I promised myself that I would photograph some of my recent projects during my maternity leave— I have schedule to shoot 4 projects in the next 2 weeks, so prepare for an overload coming soon!!

This before|after might just be my favorite yet—swipe to see!! Prior to this Master Bathroom remodel the bathroom had two small vanities, a lot of wasted space, and a toilet that left no privacy. 

This client involved me in this project from the very beginning and we created a floor plan that included every need on their list— a privacy toilet, dual shower heads, double vanity, AND a linen cabinet for storage. We used every inch of that bathroom and it somehow feels bigger!! It’s incredible what thoughtful space planning can accomplish!

a very Merry Christmas 
♡ the Magills
